 <!-- Items in scope -->
 <inscope>
   <li>assignment of a property of states;</li>
   <li>assignment of an alias identifier to states;</li>
   <li>recording of feedback related support documentation;</li>
   <li>association of supporting evidential data pertaining to states on which a justification is based;</li>
   <li>recording of the assignment of state as an activity or an event;</li>
   <li>recording of the state of resources;</li>
   <li>recording of condition parameter values evaluated for applied states;</li>   
   <li>association of requirements to states.</li>
 </inscope>

 <!-- Items out of scope -->
